14
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:10,690
[Men's 100 meters preliminaries of the Spring Track and Field Tournament]

15
00:02:22,170 --> 00:02:23,130
Qi Tian.

16
00:02:30,300 --> 00:02:31,100
Shixing.

17
00:02:49,060 --> 00:02:51,120
What is the secret you want to tell me?

18
00:03:00,740 --> 00:03:02,020
I achieved this result

19
00:03:02,020 --> 00:03:03,820
through many years of training.

20
00:03:03,850 --> 00:03:05,220
But he did it

21
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:06,360
as he stumbled,

22
00:03:06,370 --> 00:03:07,410
vomited,

23
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:08,380
