29
00:03:36,210 --> 00:03:37,740
Are you not feeling well?

30
00:03:40,150 --> 00:03:41,490
You didn't lean forward

31
00:03:41,490 --> 00:03:42,579
at the finish line.

32
00:03:42,700 --> 00:03:45,100
Besides, I've never seen you run like that.

33
00:03:46,140 --> 00:03:47,140
I had a slow start.

34
