40
00:04:15,220 --> 00:04:17,079
But I can't do that in front of you.

41
00:04:18,450 --> 00:04:20,370
The next race is

42
00:04:20,540 --> 00:04:24,100
Heat Two of men's 100 meters preliminaries.

43
00:04:36,380 --> 00:04:37,170
Luo Bing,

44
00:04:37,340 --> 00:04:38,820
