46
00:04:40,970 --> 00:04:41,780
Set!

47
00:05:12,620 --> 00:05:13,420
On your marks!

48
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:17,700
Set.

49
00:05:22,010 --> 00:05:23,210
Go, Tianfu!

50
00:05:24,140 --> 00:05:25,200
Isn't that Tianfu?

51
00:05:25,420 --> 00:05:25,940
Yeah.

52
00:05:26,260 --> 00:05:27,700
He's running so fast.

53
00:05:27,900 --> 00:05:29,600
Wu Tianfu, go!

54
00:05:31,790 --> 00:05:32,950
Come on!

55
00:05:32,980 --> 00:05:33,820
Xinghe, go!

56
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:35,600
-Go!
-Go!

57
00:05:35,850 --> 00:05:37,090
Surpass him!

58
00:05:40,490 --> 00:05:42,570
-Go, Tianfu!
-Go!

59
00:05:46,420 --> 00:05:47,900
He has completely

60
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:48,980
become a sprinter.

61
00:05:48,980 --> 00:05:50,770
He is faster than when he had a competition with you.

62
00:05:50,770 --> 00:05:51,480
Great!

63
00:06:06,110 --> 00:06:08,090
[Men's 100 meters preliminaries of the Spring Track and Field Tournament]

64
00:06:23,370 --> 00:06:24,300
Not bad.

65
00:06:24,460 --> 00:06:25,250
Impressive, Ming.

66
00:06:25,250 --> 00:06:26,140
Not bad, Tianfu.

67
00:06:26,140 --> 00:06:27,500
Not bad. 11.0 seconds.

68
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:28,610
Your personal record.

69
00:06:28,610 --> 00:06:32,010
I swear I'll set a new record of less than 11 seconds next time.

70
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:33,280
