73
00:06:42,930 --> 00:06:43,620
Tianfu,

74
00:06:43,650 --> 00:06:44,770
you performed well just now.

75
00:06:44,770 --> 00:06:45,420
Really?

76
00:06:46,550 --> 00:06:47,320
Why are you here?

77
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:48,130
Hi, Ziji.

78
00:06:48,130 --> 00:06:48,770
We came to cheer for you

79
00:06:48,770 --> 00:06:50,100
after class.

80
00:06:50,690 --> 00:06:51,659
Captain,

81
00:06:51,780 --> 00:06:53,510
don't you have training today?

82
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,540
Anyway,

83
00:06:54,540 --> 00:06:56,500
you were... an important member

84
00:06:57,470 --> 00:06:58,800
in the basketball team.

85
00:06:58,890 --> 00:07:00,480
Of course I should come here to see my former teammate.

86
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,640
That's right.

87
00:07:02,310 --> 00:07:04,440
Shasha and I are in a relationship now.

88
00:07:06,140 --> 00:07:06,950
What?

89
00:07:07,090 --> 00:07:08,750
You two are in a relationship?

90
00:07:08,940 --> 00:07:09,620
So

91
00:07:09,660 --> 00:07:11,260
you came here to watch the game with your girlfriend.

92
00:07:11,260 --> 00:07:11,980
Tianfu,

93
00:07:12,060 --> 00:07:13,410
