94
00:07:13,570 --> 00:07:14,380
Could it be...

95
00:07:14,540 --> 00:07:15,820
our get-together last time

96
00:07:15,820 --> 00:07:16,660
worked?

97
00:07:18,610 --> 00:07:20,100
Considering your appearance,

98
00:07:20,100 --> 00:07:20,620
