99
00:07:20,620 --> 00:07:22,020
right after you broke up?

100
00:07:22,450 --> 00:07:23,620
Qi Tian, watch your mouth.

101
00:07:23,620 --> 00:07:25,020
What do you mean by that?

102
00:07:27,050 --> 00:07:27,620
Ziji,

103
00:07:27,890 --> 00:07:30,380
you look very handsome in your sports uniform.

104
00:07:30,380 --> 00:07:32,420
Yes, Ziji is very handsome.

105
00:07:32,420 --> 00:07:33,659
Is he more handsome than me?

106
00:07:33,659 --> 00:07:35,590
You're... a little more handsome.

107
00:07:35,940 --> 00:07:37,620
-Come on.
-Come on.

108
00:07:37,740 --> 00:07:39,940
-So disgusting.
-So disgusting.

109
00:07:41,940 --> 00:07:43,580
The next event

110
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:45,310
is today's final event:

111
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:47,300
-The preliminary round of men's 4 x 100 m relay race...
-Fatty.

112
00:07:47,300 --> 00:07:48,860
-Get ready and warm up.
-Okay.

113
00:07:48,860 --> 00:07:49,820
A total of 18 university teams

114
00:07:49,820 --> 00:07:51,940
will participate.

115
00:07:51,940 --> 00:07:52,340
Sir.

116
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:54,220
-There will be three heats.
-Should I warm up my hands

117
00:07:54,220 --> 00:07:57,750
-or feet?
-The top 8 teams will take part in the finals tomorrow.

118
00:08:05,730 --> 00:08:07,660
We've finally gathered everyone.

119
00:08:08,540 --> 00:08:09,740
Fei Zhe would be happy

120
00:08:09,970 --> 00:08:11,100
if he could see this.

121
00:08:11,940 --> 00:08:13,060
I bought this pair of shoes

122
00:08:13,060 --> 00:08:14,570
with him.

123
00:08:15,900 --> 00:08:17,500
He didn't wear them for long.

124
00:08:18,500 --> 00:08:19,210
After that,

125
00:08:19,780 --> 00:08:21,290
as long as there is a competition,

126
00:08:21,290 --> 00:08:22,550
I'd bring them with me.

127
00:08:23,100 --> 00:08:24,140
I always think

128
00:08:24,980 --> 00:08:26,120
I can show him around

129
00:08:27,420 --> 00:08:29,150
and let him see more in this way.

130
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:33,690
I think

131
00:08:34,039 --> 00:08:35,510
I can run faster later.

132
00:08:35,539 --> 00:08:36,419
It's the preliminary round.

133
00:08:36,419 --> 00:08:38,020
We should save our strength.

134
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,460
Don't break the rules.

135
00:08:39,700 --> 00:08:40,630
Qi Tian is right.

136
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:44,300
I can't wait anymore.

137
00:08:46,530 --> 00:08:47,220
Let's go.

138
00:08:47,420 --> 00:08:48,900
Let's defeat them all.

139
00:08:52,700 --> 00:08:53,340
Yiran,

140
00:08:53,620 --> 00:08:54,220
the coach said

141
00:08:54,220 --> 00:08:56,330
you don't need to participate in the preliminary round later.

142
00:08:56,330 --> 00:08:57,100
Well...

143
00:08:58,900 --> 00:09:00,760
Then who will be the first runner?

144
00:09:01,420 --> 00:09:03,000
Wu Tianfu will be the first runner.

145
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,900
I'll be the second runner.

146
00:09:03,900 --> 00:09:04,830
Ai Ziji will be the third runner.

147
00:09:04,830 --> 00:09:06,690
Qi Tian will be the fourth runner.

148
00:09:08,740 --> 00:09:09,980
With our strength,

149
00:09:09,980 --> 00:09:11,300
we can definitely make it to the top 8 teams.

150
00:09:11,300 --> 00:09:12,780
R-Really?

151
00:09:12,900 --> 00:09:14,020
But why?

152
00:09:14,580 --> 00:09:15,900
There is nothing wrong with Yiran

153
00:09:15,900 --> 00:09:17,980
participating in the preliminary round, right?

154
00:09:17,980 --> 00:09:20,460
Maybe the coach wants to save our strength.

155
00:09:20,670 --> 00:09:21,700
Everyone knows

156
00:09:21,700 --> 00:09:22,890
Xue Yiran's strength.

157
00:09:22,890 --> 00:09:24,090
What's there to hide?

158
00:09:24,980 --> 00:09:26,660
Let's obey the coach's order.

159
00:09:27,700 --> 00:09:28,500
Qi Tian,

160
00:09:29,010 --> 00:09:31,410
I'm counting on you to make it to the finals.

161
00:09:34,380 --> 00:09:34,910
Let's go.

162
00:10:12,500 --> 00:10:15,040
Why doesn't Xue Yiran participate at this critical moment?

163
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:16,300
I also want to know why.

164
00:10:18,210 --> 00:10:19,210
What happened?

165
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:21,220
Did Fatty

166
00:10:21,220 --> 00:10:22,480
come to the wrong race?

167
00:10:24,410 --> 00:10:26,520
Could it be that he's an all-rounder?

168
00:10:32,620 --> 00:10:35,420
Could it be that Xinghe's coach has noticed it too?

169
00:10:46,410 --> 00:10:49,340
Shengling's Zeng Shixing is not on the track either.

170
00:10:49,410 --> 00:10:50,210
Could it be...

171
00:10:50,490 --> 00:10:52,750
both coaches are saving their strength?

172
00:11:26,700 --> 00:11:27,630
You're leaving?

173
00:11:29,130 --> 00:11:31,370
You don't want to participate in the 4 x 100 m relay race?

174
00:11:31,370 --> 00:11:33,300
If I can't even win in the 100 m race,

175
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:36,830
what's the point of participating in the 4 x 100 m relay race?

176
00:11:39,910 --> 00:11:41,070
I thought Xing would participate

177
00:11:41,070 --> 00:11:42,400
to compete with Xinghe.

178
00:11:47,540 --> 00:11:48,810
You performed well in the past

179
00:11:48,810 --> 00:11:49,740
even without me and Xing.

180
00:11:49,740 --> 00:11:50,580
So don't panic

181
00:11:50,580 --> 00:11:53,240
just because Xing won't participate this time.

182
00:11:58,330 --> 00:11:59,590
Our opponent this time

183
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:00,850
is not Shenglin,

184
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,270
but ourselves.

185
00:12:04,660 --> 00:12:05,880
So

186
00:12:06,060 --> 00:12:07,500
don't make any mistake.

187
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:09,380
Leave the final part to me.

188
00:12:10,830 --> 00:12:12,150
Shenglin is the best!

189
00:12:15,820 --> 00:12:16,660
-Go!
-Go!

190
00:12:24,660 --> 00:12:27,620
Today's final event is about to begin.

191
00:12:28,230 --> 00:12:30,230
Track One: North China University.

192
00:12:31,010 --> 00:12:32,810
Track Two: Huainan University.

193
00:12:36,390 --> 00:12:38,310
Track Three: Xinghe University.

194
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:42,260
Track Four: Agriculture and Forestry University.

195
00:12:42,980 --> 00:12:44,970
Track Five: Shenglin University.

196
00:12:48,490 --> 00:12:49,660
On your marks!

197
00:12:57,060 --> 00:12:57,790
Set!

198
00:13:03,860 --> 00:13:08,020
-Go!
-Go!

199
00:13:08,050 --> 00:13:10,100
Come on, boys!

200
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:11,640
-Go!
-Go!

201
00:13:22,260 --> 00:13:24,180
Go, Wu Tianfu!

202
00:13:24,950 --> 00:13:26,150
Go!

203
00:13:26,300 --> 00:13:27,810
Hurry!

204
00:13:29,380 --> 00:13:30,660
This is the first time I see such a fat guy

205
00:13:30,660 --> 00:13:31,780
in a track event.

206
00:13:32,250 --> 00:13:33,340
Fatty is still fast

207
00:13:33,340 --> 00:13:34,600
on the football field.

208
00:13:37,140 --> 00:13:38,860
Fatty, run faster!

209
00:13:39,300 --> 00:13:41,260
-Huainan, go!
-Huainan!

210
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,230
Forget what I said.

211
00:13:43,230 --> 00:13:44,110
Sorry, Fatty.

212
00:13:45,260 --> 00:13:46,540
I've rested for long.

213
00:13:46,970 --> 00:13:48,650
It's finally my turn to run.

214
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:53,860
Ziji!

215
00:13:54,060 --> 00:13:56,650
-Ziji, come on!
-Ziji, come on!

216
00:13:56,680 --> 00:13:58,030
Cool, Ziji!

217
00:13:58,760 --> 00:13:59,810
Is he Ziji?

218
00:14:00,060 --> 00:14:01,660
His hair is too ethereal.

219
00:14:01,660 --> 00:14:03,700
He's definitely the neatest among stinky men

220
00:14:03,700 --> 00:14:05,250
and the manliest among all the neat men.

221
00:14:05,250 --> 00:14:05,890
When the race is over,

222
00:14:05,890 --> 00:14:07,100
I'll ask him what shampoo he uses.

223
00:14:07,100 --> 00:14:08,360
I'll go with you later.

224
00:14:09,250 --> 00:14:10,330
Come on, Ai Ziji!

225
00:14:10,490 --> 00:14:12,380
Be worthy of the title I gave you.

226
00:14:27,100 --> 00:14:29,020
What a wonderful game!

227
00:14:38,650 --> 00:14:39,500
Frizzle.

228
00:14:39,500 --> 00:14:40,460
Hold tight!

229
00:14:41,370 --> 00:14:43,470
Come on!

230
00:14:57,990 --> 00:15:00,810
[Men's 100 meters preliminaries of the Spring Track and Field Tournament]

231
00:15:24,910 --> 00:15:25,670
We made it to the finals.

232
00:15:25,670 --> 00:15:26,800
Do our best in the finals, guys!

233
00:15:26,800 --> 00:15:28,520
-Go!
-Go!

234
00:15:28,790 --> 00:15:30,770
I knew we could definitely make it to the finals.

235
00:15:30,770 --> 00:15:33,100
But I didn't expect you to perform so well.

236
00:15:38,900 --> 00:15:40,490
Today is a perfect day.

237
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:42,310
Qi Tian won the first place in the preliminary round.

238
00:15:42,310 --> 00:15:44,470
Besides, I set my personal record.

239
00:15:44,740 --> 00:15:45,480
We also made it to the finals

240
00:15:45,480 --> 00:15:46,880
of the 4 x 100 m relay race.

241
00:15:47,110 --> 00:15:48,090
I can't wait

242
00:15:48,090 --> 00:15:49,700
to watch the game tomorrow.

243
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:51,680
Who would have thought I could participate?

244
00:15:51,680 --> 00:15:53,470
Sir, you are amazing.

245
00:15:53,620 --> 00:15:55,020
I made the best of a loser.

246
00:15:56,100 --> 00:15:57,960
Sorry. It was a slip of the tongue.

247
00:15:58,370 --> 00:15:59,900
I made the most of everyone.

248
00:16:00,250 --> 00:16:01,780
I made the most of everyone.

249
00:16:03,580 --> 00:16:04,260
Everyone,

250
00:16:04,520 --> 00:16:05,560
our coach said

251
00:16:05,790 --> 00:16:07,000
in future competitions,

252
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,110
as long as I'm qualified,

253
00:16:08,110 --> 00:16:09,570
he'll let me participate.

254
00:16:10,090 --> 00:16:11,570
So, thank you.

255
00:16:12,150 --> 00:16:13,350
If it weren't for you,

256
00:16:13,510 --> 00:16:14,220
I might have

257
00:16:14,220 --> 00:16:15,710
given up fighting for a chance today.

258
00:16:15,710 --> 00:16:16,940
You are the best sprinter

259
00:16:16,940 --> 00:16:18,090
in your team.

260
00:16:18,310 --> 00:16:19,970
No need to belittle yourself.

261
00:16:21,060 --> 00:16:23,330
After I go back later, I'll continue to practice

262
00:16:23,330 --> 00:16:25,660
to prepare for the relay finals tomorrow.

263
00:16:26,980 --> 00:16:28,020
Enough.

264
00:16:28,770 --> 00:16:30,010
Stop practicing.

265
00:16:30,030 --> 00:16:31,690
The competition is tomorrow.

266
00:16:31,870 --> 00:16:32,820
Today,

267
00:16:33,140 --> 00:16:35,140
go relax yourselves.

268
00:16:35,640 --> 00:16:36,180
Yes.

269
00:16:36,340 --> 00:16:37,150
I suggest

270
00:16:37,490 --> 00:16:37,860
we should have a bath tonight

271
00:16:37,860 --> 00:16:39,320
in my family's bathhouse.

272
00:16:39,420 --> 00:16:40,950
I'll treat you to a massage.

273
00:16:41,310 --> 00:16:42,480
I think it's a good idea.

274
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:43,680
Last time,

275
00:16:43,740 --> 00:16:45,760
Tianfu didn't give us many bath coupons.

276
00:16:45,760 --> 00:16:47,360
He only gave one to each of us.

277
00:16:47,700 --> 00:16:48,180
I...

278
00:16:48,210 --> 00:16:49,800
I didn't have many.

279
00:16:50,920 --> 00:16:51,720
It's my fault.

280
00:16:52,460 --> 00:16:53,210
I'll tell my family

281
00:16:53,210 --> 00:16:55,940
to ask the best massage therapists to wait for us.

282
00:16:59,540 --> 00:17:00,940
Sometimes,

283
00:17:01,620 --> 00:17:03,880
don't shoulder everything by yourself.

284
00:17:04,770 --> 00:17:05,630
Thank you, Sir.

285
00:17:17,760 --> 00:17:18,560
Xue Yiran,

